        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Estimated value. The production volume is based on the production volume of clay roof tiles in Europe (RER dataset) and the nominal GDP 2019 of the World and the European Union. The nominal (current) GDP of the EU in 2019 was 1.57E+13 US$ and global was 8.76E+13 US$.
Sources: 
[1] Value of production quantity (unit) is retrieved from EuroStat for the European Union for the year 2019, accessed on 20231010. Production quantity is 2'577'423'791 units.
"Non-refractory clay roofing tiles", EUROPEAN UNION (28), PRODQNT in units.
Industry, trade and services&gt;Statistics on the production of manufactured foods (prom)&gt;Sold production, exports and imports (ds-056120). Retrieved from: https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/DS-056120__custom_7772056/default/table?lang=en
[2] ecoinvent v2 Report 7, Buildings, Part IV, p. 25. Presumed weight per tile: 4 kg.
[3] https://data.worldbank.org/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.CD</productionVolumeComment>
